  npcName: "Kundrl\xE1r Fondr\u0161uk"
  dialogueLines:
  - "These materials didn\u2019t change on their own.\nThey reacted."
  - 'The Core reshaped everything around it.

    Not violently.

    Necessarily.'
  - "You\u2019re using what it left behind.\nThat\u2019s not an accident."
  - 'Check out the recipe page in your inventory..

    You might find something
    new there!'
  recipesToUnlock:
  - {fileID: 11400000, guid: e8a098de0aff9454aa61f728e501f75b, type: 2}
  ambientDialogue:
  - Fascinating... the molecular structure is vibrating
  - "Don\u2019t touch that! It hasn't stabilized yet."
  - "I used to think this was magic. Now I know it\u2019s just\u2026 heavy math."
  - The ore remembers what it used to be. I can hear it.
